Uses of Class
net.sourceforge.jeval.Evaluator

Packages that use Evaluator
net.sourceforge.jeval Contains the classes that make up the JEval API. 
net.sourceforge.jeval.function Contains function packages to be used by the evaluator API. 
net.sourceforge.jeval.function.math Contains the classes that make up math functions to be used by the evaluator API. 
net.sourceforge.jeval.function.string Contains the classes that make up string functions to be used by the evaluator API.
